Detailed Description

template<typename T>
class ContextualizerDataSet< T >

A specialization of DataSet which takes a DataSet and adds context to its patterns.

This object adds context to the patterns of a given DataSet. The context are adjacents patterns, at left or/and at right positions from the interesting pattern index. In the case of a border limit, the interesting pattern will be repeated.
